data.description: Build your Sanibel Island home in a very convenient Sanibel Center location that is tucked away and quiet, but close to shopping, beaches, restaurants, bike path, and the Sanibel Island Causeway. Frame home has been demolished and lot cleared and scraped. There are several restaurants and shops within walking distance, and you can pick up a bike at Billy's Rentals around the corner on Periwinkle. Shed on property is wind rated and conveys. No restrictions to parking an RV or boat on your property. Monthly rentals are allowed, and previous home had been a productive rental property.
